Company Description                    




                        Hotai Enterprises is a motor vehicle distributor in Taiwan. The company distributes car brands such as Toyota, Lexus, Hino, etc. Hotai is also involved in car renting, insurance brokerage, car financing services and car accessories through subsidiaries. The company was founded in 1947 and is headquartered in New Taipei City, China.                     


