Company Description


Hotai Motor Co., Ltd. is engaged in the manufacture and assembly of automobiles and industrial trucks. It also operates in the car rentals and used car business. The company offers automobile accessories, insurance, and loans. Its product brands include Toyota, Lexus, Hino trucks, and Toyota Industrial Equipment. The company was founded by Lei Ho Huang on September 1947 and is headquartered in Taipei, Taiwan.




